Text: No seed can I get a .2? For all ya'll that don't know it goes 100 gives a 100, then that 100 gives a 100 and on and on. Not 100 gives a 100, then leaves while the next guy has 99.8 because if the original seeder doesn't keep it alive we will all be stuck with incomplete files! Hence, the reason you end up with files that never reach a 100! Peace out!
